@startuml

top to bottom direction

UsuarioService - [Componente Usuário]
UploaderService - [Componente Uploader]
AudioService - [Componente Áudio]
[Componente Áudio] ..> UsuarioService
[Componente Áudio] ..> UploaderService
[Componente Usuário] ..> AudioService
[Componente Uploader] ..> AudioService
@enduml

